A Single Statement for Each Alternative:

  if (Boolean_Expression)
    
     Yes_Statement
  
  else
      
      No_Statement 
      
A Sequence of Statements for Each Alternative 

  if (Boolean_Expression)
    {
      Yes_Statment_1
      Yes_Statment_2
      ...
      Yes_Statment_Last
    }  
    
  else
     {
     No_Statement_1
     No_Statement_2
     ...
     No_Statement_Last
     }
      
